# PWA Icons Directory

This directory contains PWA icons for different sizes and purposes.

Required icons:
- icon-72x72.png
- icon-96x96.png
- icon-128x128.png
- icon-144x144.png
- icon-152x152.png
- icon-192x192.png
- icon-384x384.png
- icon-512x512.png

Optional icons:
- badge-72x72.png (for notifications)
- shortcut-*.png (for app shortcuts)
- splash-*.png (for iOS splash screens)

Note: Actual icon files should be added by the design team or generated from the main app icon.
